  "title": "connectStats nbhits not returning correct count",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nBug\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nnbHits for connectStats is returning more counts than what algolia index shows on the dashboard for that specific facet.\r\n\r\nMore specifically, for us we are getting around 9 additional hits than we should be compared to what is showing up in algolia dashboard.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nnbHits for connectStats should return the same count as dashboard for a facet\r\n\r\n**Bug: What browsers are impacted? Which versions?**\r\nTested on chrome\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\nv3.3.0",
